              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-start">
              <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-foreground">Audi A4 2020</h3>
              <p class="text-success font-bold mb-2">
                <span class="line-through text-muted-foreground font-normal me-2">‚Ç¨28,900</span>
