          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Instant Telegram Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Receive immediate notifications with vehicle photos, pricing, location, and contact details. Be the first to respond to great deals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll" data-delay="200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-primary"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 6h18l-2 13H5L3 6z"/><path d="M3 6L2.25 4H1"/><circle cx="9" cy="20" r="1"/><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="1"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Advanced Filtering</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Set detailed criteria including make, model, year, price range, mileage, fuel type, and location to find exactly what you need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll" data-delay="300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-primary"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12,6 12,12 16,14"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">24/7 Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Our system works around the clock, checking for new listings and price changes so you never miss an opportunity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll" data-delay="400">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-primary"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Limited slots ensure you stay ahead of the competition. Perfect for dealers where being first means the difference between profit and loss.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll" data-delay="500">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-primary"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M21 12c.552 0 1-.448 1-1V8c0-.552-.448-1-1-1H3c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v3c0 .552.448 1 1 1h18z"/><path d="M3 12v7c0 .552.448 1 1 1h16c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-7"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Flexible Management</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Pause or cancel your subscription anytime. Modify your search criteria as your needs change. Complete control at your fingertips.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-muted">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">How Amiquus Works</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">Get started in minutes and begin receiving alerts for your perfect vehicles.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center relative animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-4">Set Your Criteria</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Define your search parameters including vehicle type, price range, location, and other specific requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center relative animate-on-scroll" data-delay="100">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-4">Connect Telegram</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Link your Telegram account to receive instant notifications. Setup takes less than 2 minutes with our guided process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center relative animate-on-scroll" data-delay="200">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-4">Choose Monitoring Frequency</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Select how often we check for new listings. Higher frequencies give you faster alerts and better competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-8 text-center relative animate-on-scroll" data-delay="300">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
